                      "code" : ".sourcekit-lsp\/config.json",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " file for the selected project(s). The generated configuration file will be pre-populated with the JSON schema for the version of the Swift toolchain that is being used. Use the ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code" : "swift.sourcekit-lsp.configurationBranch",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " setting to pin the SourceKit-LSP branch that the schema comes from.",
                      "type" : "text"
